ZH: 我们相见的时候已经很晚了。
EN: It was already late when we met.
ZH: 他们终于相见了，心里非常高兴。
EN: They finally met each other and were very happy.
ZH: 我们约定在陌生的城市相见。
EN: We agreed to meet in a unfamiliar city.
ZH: 两位老朋友相见的时候，互相握手致意。
EN: When the two old friends met, they shook hands and greeted each other.
ZH: 我们相见的地点是在咖啡馆。
EN: The place where we meet is a coffee shop.
ZH: 你忘了我们上周相见的约定吗？
EN: Did you forget our meeting arrangement last week?
ZH: 他们约好明天中午相见。
EN: They arranged to meet tomorrow at noon.
ZH: 我们可不可以改一下相见的时间？
EN: Can we change the time of our meeting?
ZH: 我们下个月相见，你要请我吃饭。
EN: When we meet next month, you have to treat me to a meal.
ZH: 昨晚我和老朋友相见了，我们聊了很多。
EN: Last night I met an old friend, and we chatted a lot.
ZH: 我会直接去机场，然后我们在那相见吗？
EN: Shall I go directly to the airport, and we meet there?
ZH: 他们在那儿相见了好几次。
EN: They met there several times.
ZH: 我和她相见的时候，才发现她有多美。
EN: When I met her, I realized how beautiful she was.
ZH: 请提前告诉我什么时候我们可以相见。
EN: Please let me know in advance when we can meet.
ZH: 明天见，愿我们再相见时都能有好运。
EN: See you tomorrow, may we all have good luck when we meet again.
ZH: 我们终于相见了！好久没有见到你了。
EN: We finally meet! It's been a long time since I saw you.
ZH: 如果你们下周来北京，我们可以相见。
EN: If you come to Beijing next week, we can meet.
ZH: 我们今天中午有时间相见吗？
EN: Do we have time to meet today at noon?
ZH: 不好意思，我无法和你相见。
EN: Sorry, I can't meet you.
ZH: 虽然我们只在网上交流，但我很期待与你相见。
EN: Although we only communicate online, I look forward to meeting you.
